    {
        "content": "<p>It sounds like you're asking about making tactic macros.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">macro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"the_great_tactic_of_mr_proof\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tactic</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">`</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">tactic</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;-</span><span class=\"n\">Real</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sq_sqrt</span><span class=\"o\">])</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Then <code>the_great_tactic_of_mr_proof</code> is <code>rw [&lt;-Real.sq_sqrt]</code> for short.</p>",
